            <a class="col-12 mt-5" href="
            {{ path('page_318', {'heroId':heroId }) }}
            ">
                <img class="fleches" src="{{ asset ('assets/img/ArrowR.png') }}" />
            </a>
            {# turn to 318. #}
    </p>
    </br>
    <p>If you wish to run for cover in the trees. 
